                <div class="6u 12u$(medium)">
                    <header class="major">
                        <h2>RiskID application<br />
                        </h2>
                    </header>
                    <p>RiskID is a visual analytics tool that combines visualization components
			with clustering analysis techniques to assist the user
			in the process of labeling network traffic connections for generating high
			quality dataset. RiskID relies on the concept of behavioral models and the
			letter representation models developed as part of the 
			<a href="https://stratosphereips.org/">Stratosphere Intrusion Prevention
                            System (IPS)</a>. For more information about the letter representation model visit <a href="/users/letter"> the following explanation section </a></p>.

                </div>
