                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="6u$ 12u$(medium)">
                    <header class="major">
                        <h2>Main Visual Components<br />
                        </h2>
                    </header>
                    <p>
                        A Connection List to show the connections grouped according with their encoding behavior similarity.
                        Several filtering options to customize the output.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        A Traffic light metaphor to represent current connection label: red circle means ”Botnet”, green circle means ”Normal” and yellow circle means ”Unlabeled”.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        A Heatmap to easily recognize the predominant features from each connection and those related connections with similar features.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Charts to describe the frequency of occurrence of the different letters from the behavioral encoding and the periodicity feature distribution.
                    </p>
                    <header class="major">
                        <h2>Main features: Label Probability and Ordering by Similarity with the selected Connection <br />
                        </h2>
                    </header>
                    <p>
                        A bar for suggesting the label probability for unlabeled connections. 
                    </p>

                    <p>
                        Reordering the connection list when an unlabeled connection is selected. Reordering is done by similarity with the selected connection.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
